The paper deals with measuring the similarity of polygonal curves, which is a problem in computational geometry (cs.CG). The paper introduces new data structures and algorithms for computing Fr\'echet distance, which is a problem in data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.DM). The paper also mentions handling noise, which is a problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV).
